      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 632,
      "message": "The mariadb docker is designed to automatically create the user/password and database for you if MYSQL_USER, MYSQL_PASSWORD and MYSQL_DATABASE are set.  We should really update our database init script so it can be run without admin privs, since in some envs, we will have the mysql root password.",
